description:
How we treat others matters, and Jesus emphasizes this lesson while teaching His disciples in Matthews Sermon on the Mount. The secret to a successful Christian life is simple: loving and treating others well. #Shorts #YouTubeShorts 

To watch the full video from Elder Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, paste this link into your browser: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9STdjlXEiCo&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=44
